Suspend and Resume an Orchestration

You started your loan processing orchestration, but your customer wants to pause the process. Now you can suspend a running orchestration, and when the customer has updated their documentation, you can resume the orchestration.

Where: This change applies to Lightning Experience in Enterprise, Performance, Unlimited, and Developer editions.

Who: Users with the Manage Orchestration Runs user permission or the Manage Orchestration Runs and Work Items user permission.

How: To suspend an orchestration run, locate the orchestration run you want to suspend from the Orchestration Runs list view, select Suspend Run. To resume a suspended orchestration run, locate the suspended orchestration run you want to resume from the Orchestration Runs list view, select Resume Run.
